snippet: Michael Bennett and the Seattle Seahawks reached agreement on a three-year contract extension on Friday that will keep the defensive end under contract through the 2020 season....
lead_paragraph: Michael Bennett and the Seattle Seahawks reached agreement on a three-year contract extension on Friday that will keep the defensive end under contract through the 2020 season.

headline.main: Seattle's Michael Bennett Reaches 3-Year Contract Extension
headline.print_headline: Seattle's Michael Bennett Reaches 3-Year Contract Extension
